---
---

<section id="proyecto" class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-dark-bg">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text">
        Un PMS construido desde la operación real
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2 leading-relaxed">
        Trabaje más de 10 años en recepción de hotel. Conocí cada dolor operativo.
        Cuando aprendí a programar, decidí resolverlos todos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-surface-200 dark:border-dark-border hover:border-brand-300 dark:hover:border-brand-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-layer1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-brand-100 dark:group-hover:bg-brand-900/30 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text mb-2">Problema real</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Hojas de cálculo, WhatsApp, papeles sueltos. La operación diaria de un hotel
          depende de herramientas que no fueron diseñadas para eso.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-surface-200 dark:border-dark-border hover:border-brand-300 dark:hover:border-brand-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-layer1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-brand-100 dark:group-hover:bg-brand-900/30 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text mb-2">Solución con código</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Un sistema centralizado que reemplaza Excel, los grupos de WhatsApp
          y los cuadernos de notas por módulos digitales integrados.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-surface-200 dark:border-dark-border hover:border-brand-300 dark:hover:border-brand-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-layer1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-brand-100 dark:group-hover:bg-brand-900/30 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text mb-2">Documentado aquí</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Cada decisión técnica, cada error, cada solución. No es un tutorial genérico:
          es el diario de construcción de un producto real.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
